{"tid":899531,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"發生咗呢D事，我唔知點面對我個仔同老公","createTime":"2018-11-12T13:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T01:42:44.000Z","uid":87515,"like":5,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bd8e192be79d635f38f0a2748c1aae5853dcd5fd","tid":899531,"uid":87515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T13:39:22.000Z","msg":"成件事我都係為囝囝好，無諗過會搞到咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事緣我囝囝一直都有個秘密瞞住我地<br />\n以前成日返工OT，唔得閒陪個仔同老公<br />\n佢中學個陣成績差，而且成日同男仔fd玩得好埋，咁我起初都唔為意<br />\n直至佢入大學之後，比我見到佢同個男仔繞哂手咁<br />\n我就開始懷疑自己個仔既性向，但係一時之間又唔知點算好，於是就打比個係學校做老師既朋友問<br />\n佢同我講千其唔好鬧個仔，要比多D關懷，多D同個仔接觸，慢慢開導佢<br />\n仲話以前見過個學生同我個仔差唔多情形，而家咪一樣有女朋友<br />\n<br />\n我搵左一晚入囝囝間房同佢傾下，咁我都識做既，咪問下佢大學識左D咩朋友呀，有無比人蝦呀<br />\n佢就好驚青咁答無呀，都係D普通朋友，有男有女囉，咁我都無再問落去，剩係攬住囝囝，話有咩事可以同媽咪講<br />\n<br />\n之後囝囝就帶左個女仔返黎，睇落都幾乖，食完飯會主動幫手，咁我都幾安慰，我仲靜靜雞問個女仔諗住幾時結婚<br />\n<br />\n之後個仔開始返工，咁我就辭左份工轉做全職主婦，係屋企既時間多左，老公又唔得閒，於是咪出去shopping<br />\n點知比我見到囝囝個女朋友同第二個男人一齊，我跟住佢地到酒店門口先知道咩事<br />\n<br />\n個晚，我坐係客廳等，唔知點開口，囝囝好夜先返黎，仲有D酒氣，咁我問佢做咩咁夜返呀，佢咩都無講<br />\n我企起身話煲番熱D湯，突然，囝囝係後面攬住我，話唔知點算好，咁我就摸下囝囝錫左佢一啖，佢又攬住我黎係咁錫，跟往我地入左囝囝間房，做左D對唔住老公既事<br />\n個一刻，我知道囝囝好唔開心，好想幫佢分擔下，我咩都無講，由囝囝射入去，咁多年無做過愛，而家終於有番當年同老公做既興奮<br />\n之後幫囝囝蓋被先返房訓<br />\n<br />\n過咗個禮拜，我發覺時不時唔舒服，去左睇醫生，於是...<br />\n<br />\n而家老公問我肚入面係邊個經手，我唔敢講<br />\n所以想問下各位應該點做"},{"pid":"724a6221bc30643c5a294abcc4e7903d3ef0b600","tid":899531,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T13:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e793fa5d1e4a33756a87c52499f92f3ba4365b2","tid":899531,"uid":143288,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T13:56:40.000Z","msg":"廢事比"},{"pid":"c984b597f6c0300bd65c0ca156533217289e60bd","tid":899531,"uid":3167,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T14:04:28.000Z","msg":"又扑一個on9"},{"pid":"629d7a399554c1179a657d85b2875ed5daf14049","tid":899531,"uid":213332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T14:08:39.000Z","msg":"可唔可以.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nshare 條片出黎"},{"pid":"67dc19352be98b6164de995b0b1dd0be65f0b045","tid":899531,"uid":68641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T14:12:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee6d3af3add6cf1a3363959c39c156b5e55ac75","tid":899531,"uid":154106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T16:55:11.000Z","msg":"重作啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96317ade902b9b56863159f5bf3ffa91979ca2ad","tid":899531,"uid":27305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T17:12:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">閱</span>"},{"pid":"9009f4dfe92f3d987388169721068644dd27da7d","tid":899531,"uid":48631,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T17:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/13/011702_7d8953d94ba899db9effaae34c7e1dcd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F13%2F011702_7d8953d94ba899db9effaae34c7e1dcd.png&h=afa2415a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主睇黎你戀母情義結好撚嚴重喎,我真係驚你有一日上鳩你自己老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4d2bf3b740812a695abb02fe6e0429183ef990","tid":899531,"uid":138860,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T17:27:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"106cde8ec73c695b7166fc5465b2a7eb510b0fef","tid":899531,"uid":219614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T17:30:13.000Z","msg":"放個report上黎先考慮接納你既供詞"},{"pid":"84dffdce5d436f3c1d4adaaf21367179f649554b","tid":899531,"uid":54930,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T17:30:19.000Z","msg":"<strong>好明顯呢個係一個無聊兼夾on9既post,回既人只會助長佢<br />\n當然我都無咁蠢,要好好咁資源運用 </strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://lh4.ggpht.com/_9SXYyMTt_Ig/TFbDEmmb1bI/AAAAAAAACDA/7lCmHDa4cSA/P1150144.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flh4.ggpht.com%2F_9SXYyMTt_Ig%2FTFbDEmmb1bI%2FAAAAAAAACDA%2F7lCmHDa4cSA%2FP1150144.JPG&h=d492a178&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://lh6.ggpht.com/_9SXYyMTt_Ig/TFbDEoQ5sgI/AAAAAAAACDI/44YH52m9qOo/3823902124_74b33edfcf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flh6.ggpht.com%2F_9SXYyMTt_Ig%2FTFbDEoQ5sgI%2FAAAAAAAACDI%2F44YH52m9qOo%2F3823902124_74b33edfcf.jpg&h=cf310693&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://lh5.ggpht.com/_9SXYyMTt_Ig/TFbDEkVkl3I/AAAAAAAACDE/1t-RMlIhwBo/0065MR809A927D3642F317m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flh5.ggpht.com%2F_9SXYyMTt_Ig%2FTFbDEkVkl3I%2FAAAAAAAACDE%2F1t-RMlIhwBo%2F0065MR809A927D3642F317m.jpg&h=a36e97ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://lh5.ggpht.com/_9SXYyMTt_Ig/TFbDEkKU05I/AAAAAAAACDM/iQAsD2-5E3U/s800/10107500062_127.0.0.1_109911241110.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flh5.ggpht.com%2F_9SXYyMTt_Ig%2FTFbDEkKU05I%2FAAAAAAAACDM%2FiQAsD2-5E3U%2Fs800%2F10107500062_127.0.0.1_109911241110.jpg&h=53dca9f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我每食完一碟火腩飯之後都會同我女朋友講分手<br />\n因為我知道, 佢已經唔再明白我<br />\n<br />\n佢唔知道我o係茶記所經歷過既有幾多<br />\n<br />\n佢問我食乜, 我真係唔想答佢<br />\n日本野? 秦國野? 真係敷淺<br />\n究竟我仲可以繼續忍受自己既伴侶將d生既肉放入口<br />\n每舊火腩都經過紅紅烈火，百度高溫<br />\n係經過歷煉, 係經過漫長既試鍊<br />\n每一舊都有佢既歷史，佢既故事<br />\n魚生究竟有d乜? 根本就好似d白痴港女錦, 一無所知, 戇鳩鳩, 生勾勾<br />\n<br />\n我恨我既人生唔可以好似火腩錦<br />\n搵到咁多好既伴侶, 豆腐, 涼瓜, 冬瓜, 枝竹..各有特色<br />\n亦搵唔到咁多知音人,<br />\n<br />\n有時侯, 我自己一個坐o係茶記食火腩飯<br />\n我覺得自己係孤獨, 我覺得呢個世界係冇人明白我<br />\n我叫左枝青島, 我望住杯入面黃色既啤酒<br />\n我望唔透, 我望唔清究竟呢個世界仲有幾多野我係掌握到<br />\n我好迷茫<br />\n<br />\n我離開間茶記, 我俾錢既時侯發覺有個OL食緊枝竹火腩飯<br />\n我望住佢, 佢望住我<br />\n我地互相點點頭<br />\n我好感動, 原來呢個世界仲有人係同我有相同既諗法<br />\n我忍住淚水<br />\n走出茶記, 點起支煙,<br />\n頭都冇回就走返屋企<br />\n或者個OL會問, 點解我放棄呢一段咁難得既姻緣<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道<br />\no係呢一刻<br />\n我覺得我係一個浪子<br />\n<br />\n<strong>推廣下火腩飯先<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/%E7%81%AB%E8%85%A9%E9%A3%AF%E6%BD%AE%E6%96%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%2581%25AB%25E8%2585%25A9%25E9%25A3%25AF%25E6%25BD%25AE%25E6%2596%2587&d=zKUfNEAgjCwU09ksVv1QEC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=5b3cd9a5\" target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/%E7%81%AB%E8%85%A9%E9%A3%AF%E6%BD%AE%E6%96%87</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">亦請呢個回應以下既會員唔好再回應啦</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"dbc507e1b9842de1ad9c19504a57bfc29627443d","tid":899531,"uid":87515,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9009f4dfe92f3d987388169721068644dd27da7d","tid":899531,"uid":48631,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T17:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/13/011702_7d8953d94ba899db9effaae34c7e1dcd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F13%2F011702_7d8953d94ba899db9effaae34c7e1dcd.png&h=afa2415a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主睇黎你戀母情義結好撚嚴重喎,我真係驚你有一日上鳩你自己老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T17:57:12.000Z","msg":"我係用囝囝個帳號<br />\n<br />\n乜原來我個囝囝成日搵埋呢D野㗎"},{"pid":"c203b9574c3afa84479be4d6ba64fef8b73fa231","tid":899531,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T23:00:42.000Z","msg":"仲以為係7年sp bb 既老母視角"},{"pid":"bfac8a771a1863e8a635484ab530af0c2e707e9e","tid":899531,"uid":161462,"like"